Class TailwindEventManager

java.lang.Object
com.jackmeng.halcyoninae.tailwind.TailwindEventManager
public class TailwindEventManager extends Object
A global scoped targeted towards managing multiple Listeners for the BigContainer player all at the same time without having to hold multiple Lists directly.

3.1
Author:
